{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "55885cef-8a3d-4882-a98e-ab14ad7e322d",
    "name": "CRA API - Complete Tests",
    "description": "Collection complete des endpoints CRA.\n\nPre-requis importants:\n1) Connecte-toi d'abord avec 'Login Admin' pour remplir {{admin_token}} automatiquement.\n2) Les endpoints /api/cra/** exigent un token ROLE_COLLABORATEUR ({{collaborateur_token}}).\n3) Regle metier: la saisie CRA (remplir/update/soumettre) est autorisee uniquement entre le 22 et le 28 (timezone Europe/Paris), sauf cas REJECTED.\n4) Lors de la creation d'un collaborateur, renseigne {{collaborateur_password}}: ce mot de passe pourra ensuite etre utilise pour le login collaborateur.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 - Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "let data = {};",
                  "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
                  "if (data.token) { pm.environment.set('admin_token', data.token); }",
                  "if (data.role) { pm.environment.set('admin_role', data.role); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{admin_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "description": "Recupere et stocke automatiquement {{admin_token}}."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login Collaborateur",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "let data = {};",
                  "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
                  "if (data.token) { pm.environment.set('collaborateur_token', data.token); }",
                  "if (data.role) { pm.environment.set('collaborateur_role', data.role); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{collaborateur_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{collaborateur_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "description": "Recupere et stocke automatiquement {{collaborateur_token}}."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "10 - Admin / Collaborateurs",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Lister Collaborateurs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/collaborateurs"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Creer Collaborateur",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.environment.set('collaborateur_email', 'collab.' + Date.now() + '@cbx.com');",
                  "if (!pm.environment.get('collaborateur_password')) {",
                  "  pm.environment.set('collaborateur_password', 'Collab123!');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "let data = {};",
                  "try { data = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
                  "if (data.id) { pm.environment.set('collaborateur_id', String(data.id)); }",
                  "if (data.email) { pm.environment.set('collaborateur_email', data.email); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nom\": \"Dupont\",\n  \"prenom\": \"Jean\",\n  \"email\": \"{{collaborateur_email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{collaborateur_password}}\",\n  \"contrat\": \"CDI\",\n  \"seniorite\": \"JUNIOR\",\n  \"salaire\": \"35000\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/collaborateurs"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Collaborateur By Id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/collaborateurs/{{collaborateur_id}}"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Collaborateur",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{admin_token}}"
